model: Mirai Back to the Future Concept
description: At the end of the first Back to the Future movie, Doc Brown brought back a Mr. Fusion reactor that could convert trash into energy from the future. Toyota wanted to prove a point - that the Mirai had achieved what the Mr Reactor did, so in collaboration with a custom shop called MV Designs and Mark Wu they created an homage to the original time-travelling Delorean, complete with gullwing doors and a Mr Fusion unit in the trunk.
creator: Keanny
